  <Content>I received a letter from a little girl name Kalliope a few suns ago. I'm not quite certain how to aid her, but I wanted to share it with you:

"Dear Eeva,

A Deoch ago, I found a baby mouse behind one of the ale barrels in the Undine Tavern. I knew Chloe would have gotten rid of him if she knew, so I made him a new home outside behind the tavern in one of the bushes. I always brought him scraps of food, and kept him warm with some of the rags that were going to be thrown out. I named him Pudgy, and I have had him ever since.

