Damara's old cat got sick once, and it refused to eat or drink for days. But Pudgy is still eating as much as before, if not more.
I really don't know what to think. I can't tell Chloe, because she would get mad at me for keeping it.

Do you think you could help me?

Hopeful,
Kalliope"


Perhaps you could visit her and see what you can do for her. Kalliope is usually at the tavern in Undine.


Thank you,
Eeva
Suomi Inn Keeper

